# Agent Workflow Starter Spec

Agent Workflow Starter is a public starter repo for agent-assisted knowledge work.

## Purpose

Help a user plan, organize, execute, verify, and review work with Claude, Claude Code, GitHub, templates, checks, and lightweight workflow rules.

## Canonical order

Goal, current state, dependencies, setup/config, smallest useful unit, execution, verification, follow-ups.

## Atomic units

Atoms can be source notes, claims, sections, prompts, templates, checklist items, lesson steps, hooks, smoke checks, release notes, or small scripts.

## Setup/config

Dotfiles and hooks are setup/config. They require approval before changes.

## Advanced tools

Advanced tools are added only when repeated friction is clear and the result remains reviewable.
